data.description: **HUGE PRICE REDUCTION PLUS SELLER IS OFFERING $10,000 IN CONCESSIONS AT CLOSING**. Use this for a 2-1 Buy Down Program. Lower your payment significantly on your mortgage or use it for a permanent rate buy down, pay your closing costs or lower your price even more! **Beautiful home in west Evans in the sought after Ashcroft Heights. This home has been updated with new flooring, paint, a/c and a finished basement to name a few making it a 6 bedroom 3 bath home under 500K! The yard is an impressive size with mature fruit trees to enjoy. Perfect location close to shopping and Hwy 85 making commuting a breeze! Don't miss the opportunity to own this fabulous home.
